# Storefront Backend Project

#scripts:
-----------------
Developing: npm run start
Building: npm run build
a starter app : npm run dev
testing: npm run test

-------------------------
##connect to the database:
------------------------
connect to database => psql -U postgres
create the project database => CREATE DATABASE postgres /postgres_test
create tables => CREATE TABLE users , products , orders , order_products
connect to the project database => \c postgres/postgres_test
--------------------------------------------------
###.env
----------
POSTGRES_HOST=localhost
POSTGRES_DB=postgres
POSTGRES_USER=postgres
POSTGRES_PORT = 5432
POSTGRES_PASSWORD=shaimaa
POSTGRES_DB_TEST=postgres_test
ENV=dev

BCRYPT_PASSWORD=speak-friend-and-enter
SALT_ROUNDS=10
TOKEN_SECRET=your-secret-token
----------------------------------


### API Endpoints
#### Products
- Index GET:http://localhost:3000/products
- Show  GET:http://localhost:3000/products/id
- Create POST:http://localhost:3000/products

#### Users
- Index  GET:http://localhost:3000/users
- Show   GET:http://localhost:3000/users/id
- Create POST:http://localhost:3000/users

#### Orders
- GET:http://localhost:3000/orders

##### Order_products

- POST:http://localhost:3000/service/addProduct

## Data Shapes

#### Product
-  id
- product_name
- price


#### User
- id
- firtName
- lastName
- pwd

#### Orders
- id
- user_id
- status

##### Order_products
- id
- product_id
- quantity




